<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background: linear-gradient(to right, #0ea5e9, #0284c7); color: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; text-align: center; }
      .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
      .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-top: none; }
      .info-box { background: white; border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
      .info-row { display: flex; margin-bottom: 10px; }
      .info-label { font-weight: bold; width: 150px; color: #6b7280; }
      .info-value { color: #111827; }
      .priority-badge { display: inline-block; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; }
      .priority-low { background: #d1fae5; color: #065f46; }
      .priority-medium { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }
      .priority-high { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; }
      .priority-critical { background: #fce7f3; color: #9d174d; }
      .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🎯 Nouvel objectif assigné</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Bonjour <%= @employee.first_name %>,</p>

      <p>Un nouvel objectif vous a été assigné par <strong><%= @manager.full_name %></strong>.</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Objectif :</span>
          <span class="info-value"><strong><%= @objective.title %></strong></span>
        </div>
        <% if @objective.description.present? %>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Description :</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= @objective.description %></span>
        </div>
        <% end %>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Priorité :</span>
          <span class="info-value">
            <span class="priority-badge priority-<%= @objective.priority %>">
              <%= @objective.priority&.capitalize %>
            </span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Échéance :</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= l(@objective.deadline, format: :long) %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Assigné par :</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= @manager.full_name %></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>Cordialement,<br><strong>L'équipe Izi-RH</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Cet email a été envoyé automatiquement, merci de ne pas y répondre.</p>
      <p>&copy; <%= Date.current.year %> Izi-RH. Tous droits réservés.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
